fulltitle: Gary Bartz - "Yusef Lateef Could Really Play The Blues"
description: From "A Tribute to Yusef Lateef" The Hang, December 28, 2013, Gary Bartz remembers his first encounters with Yusef Lateef and that the late musician and teacher could really play the blues.
